snippet.title: Eat To Fight - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Download: https://eattofight.itch.io/eattofight
In Eat to Fight" the player takes control over a slimey character that doesn't have any skills except eating. By digesting food, dependent on the type of it, it temporarily unlocks skills which are necessary to beat the enemies and overcome obstacles in the unsafe world.

Credits
